<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
    }
    .container {
      width: 80%;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    h1 {
      color: #333;
    }
    p {
      color: #555;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #999;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Welcome to Our Newsletter!</h1>
    <p>Hello <%= subscriberName %>,</p>
    <p>Thank you for subscribing to our newsletter. We're excited to have you on board and look forward to sharing our updates with you.</p>
    <p>Best Regards,<br>The Newsletter Team</p>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>You are receiving this email because you subscribed to our newsletter.</p>
      <p><a href="<%= unsubscribeLink %>">Unsubscribe</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
